  36:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_spi.c ****           (##) SPI pins configuration
  37:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_spi.c ****               (+++) Enable the clock for the SPI GPIOs
  38:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_spi.c ****               (+++) Configure these SPI pins as alternate function push-pull
  39:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_spi.c ****           (##) NVIC configuration if you need to use interrupt process or DMA process
  40:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_spi.c ****               (+++) Configure the SPIx interrupt priority
