  45:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_spi.c ****               (+++) Configure the DMA handle parameters
  46:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_spi.c ****               (+++) Configure the DMA Tx or Rx Stream/Channel
