  79:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_spi.c **** 
  80:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_spi.c ****       (#) Use function HAL_SPI_UnRegisterCallback to reset a callback to the default
  81:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_spi.c ****           weak function.
