 822:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_spi.c ****     (#) APIs provided for these 2 transfer modes (Blocking mode or Non blocking mode using either I
 823:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_spi.c ****         exist for 1Line (simplex) and 2Lines (full duplex) modes.
